Package logic

Class User

java.lang.Object
logic.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
CertifiedWorker
public class User extends Object implements Serializable
The User class represents a user in the system, with attributes such as name, ID, contact details, and account information.
